OL,3,CCarer who helped husband play football
OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,FIt has meant the Newcastle United fan
OL,7,Fhas been able to keep playing the game
OL,8,Fhe loves.
OL,10,FDave had a heart attack in 2006 and
OL,11,Fsuffered an hypoxic brain injury,
OL,12,Fresulting in him losing much of his
OL,13,Fspeech and some mobility.
OL,15,FBut with Sue's help, he has been able
OL,16,Fto continue pursuing many of his
OL,17,Fhobbies and interests.
