OL,3,CCarer who helped husband play football
OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,FSue and Dave have been supported by
OL,7,Fthe brain injury charity Headway
OL,8,FTyneside for the last 10 years, and
OL,9,Fnow Jo Wallis from the charity has
OL,10,Fnominated Sue for its Carer of the
OL,11,FYear Award.
OL,13,FJo told TV Tyne Tees that it was not
OL,14,Fjust for the work Sue has done with
OL,15,FDave that she nominated her, but how
OL,16,Fshe has helped other people in a
OL,17,Fsimilar situation to herself.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
