OL,3,CCarer who helped husband play football
OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,F"It's lovely, but I was totally taken
OL,7,Fback when I was told," she said. "It's
OL,8,Fnice to know that somebody appreciates
OL,9,Fwhat you're doing because there is a
OL,10,Flot more to it than your everyday
OL,11,Fgeneral life."
OL,13,FSue is one of three finalists up for
OL,14,Fthe award in London on Thursday (5
OL,15,FDecember).
